    <item>
      <title>fonts</title>
      <link>/braindump/posts/2025-08-01_19-21-49-fonts/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/braindump/posts/2025-08-01_19-21-49-fonts/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A computer font is implemented as a digital data file containing a set of graphically related glyphs. A computer font is designed and created using a font editor. A computer font specifically designed for the computer screen, and not for printing, is a screen font.&lt;/p&gt;
